body:
### About Project
We are UCSD students taking CSE 145, an embedded systems design class. We aim to build an epileptic seizure prediction system along with our [hardware team](https://github.com/mikeanthonywild/eeg-hardware/wiki).

### Software Team
Alex Rosengarten (@alxrsngrtn), Alex Maragakis (@amaragak)
